data.description: Welcome Home to this beautiful townhome,end unit with 2 Master Bedrooms ensuite bathrooms in each bedroom and walk in closets. Open concept with plenty of sunlight. kitchen includes plenty of counter space with stainless steel appliances.  Relax and unwind on the screened-in porch. You'll have two assigned parking spaces, and a wide range of community amenities, including an outdoor pool with 5 swim lanes, a furnished clubhouse with an efficiency kitchen, picnic areas with grills, scenic pathways, playgrounds, and recreation areas. Located in Windsor Park 15 minutes from Historic downtown Wilmington. Come see what this beautiful townhouse has to offer!
